<section id="readingText">
  <p align="left">Dear Pat,</p>
  <p align="left">My English teacher has told me you're looking for a penfriend so I'm writing to introduce myself to you.</p>
  <p align="left">I'm 24 years old and I live in Hong Kong. I work in the tourist industry as a tour guide. I live with my parents on an outlying island and I travel to work by ferry every day. <font color="#0000ff">[10] my job as I get to meet so many interesting people from all over the world, but <font color="#0000ff">[11]</font> having to work on public holidays and at the weekend!</font></p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">As for my hobbies and interests, I'm a bit of a fitness fanatic! I go jogging every morning before I go to work and I always do some yoga before I go to bed. I play badminton twice a week and squash about once a fortnight. <font color="#0000ff">[12]</font> hiking and try and get out to the country park at least once a month, but <font color="#0000ff">[13]</font> going swimming in the summer because <font color="#0000ff">[14]</font> the heat. And <font color="#0000ff">[15]</font> gyms! <font color="#0000ff">[16]</font> running on a treadmill that doesn't go anywhere and staring aimlessly into space. Apart from sport, <font color="#0000ff">[17]</font> dancing and I often go clubbing with friends at the weekend. <font color="#0000ff">[18]</font> disco music and I can dance for hours.</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">Anyway, enough about me! What about you? What do you like doing in your free time? I hope you'll write soon and tell me about yourself.</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">Looking forward to hearing from you.</p>
  <p align="left">Best wishes,</p>
  <p align="left">Kim</p>
  <p align="left">
    <font size="2"/>
  </p>
</section>

